{"tid":538491,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"轉工問題好苦惱，求解答","createTime":"2018-01-23T16:02:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-25T01:21:19.000Z","uid":138225,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"a3441ce06afb6fbf4fbf8987ffdae1fd37c02ec6","tid":538491,"uid":138225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T16:02:30.000Z","msg":"話說小妹畢左業都一段時間，上星期終於搵到份工，因為上一手同事係我返工幾日後就要走，所以得幾日教晒我所有佢要做嘅野<br />\n<br />\n咁得幾日，我當然唔係好熟手啦，但佢走左，因為公司得10個人左右，所以負責呢個工作岡位嘅人其實得我一個<br />\n<br />\n問題黎啦，呢個時候我收到另一個offer，比而家多3-4k，咁我緊係想轉工啦<br />\n<br />\n但係個心就唔係好過到自己果關，覺得我做得果幾日，又係唯一一個接左手嘅同事，如果就咁走左係咪好狗？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但果邊係多3-4k<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇過來人講下走唔走好，走又應該點辭職<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申 logistic 行業，主要做聯絡supplier"},{"pid":"d54c73c3c99341c821fd2e587560da67330baebc","tid":538491,"uid":11049,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T16:02:55.000Z","msg":"走"},{"pid":"10e966fb2d70d2703f1191f34c2c5e4cae878116","tid":538491,"uid":62020,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T16:04:19.000Z","msg":"走<br />\n<br />\n到你好似我咁轉工難 就後悔"},{"pid":"e7d460fdbbc0d4ee645cd2bf537cf269c90384f0","tid":538491,"uid":85819,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T16:04:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"08697348987a0e991a110a79822ed00098b6b7bc","tid":538491,"uid":138225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d54c73c3c99341c821fd2e587560da67330baebc","tid":538491,"uid":11049,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T16:02:55.000Z","msg":"走"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T16:05:28.000Z","msg":"公司識做我呢part嘅人可能得我一個，就咁走會唔會好衰？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd0487916237c42a455fe4f5b196f9d0773aa92a","tid":538491,"uid":11049,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e