"},{"pid":"4fea231ee0fd6b76fae0877beb5509aaa3fede91","tid":538491,"uid":50818,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T16:14:46.000Z","msg":"差三四千，老西都走<br />\n話做左幾日唔適合<br />\n即日通知可以走"},{"pid":"63601c472ec92ba4754dcb4e9b725e2f12dbf4be","tid":538491,"uid":57462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T16:15:43.000Z","msg":"轉啦 唔好睇到自己咁重要"},{"pid":"864d70da657d27ee4ddf7a87e44e164c2f55ea09","tid":538491,"uid":120983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bfe8c275203461fdbfe5fc5e4c896fee1eb45de2","tid":538491,"uid":138225,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T16:13:04.000Z","msg":"咁我要點辭職先冇咁尷尬？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T16:16:04.000Z","msg":"中左3t六合彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"791cf40aef9272fccde53fcf5e81f58ad809fd2f","tid":538491,"uid":100131,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bfe8c275203461fdbfe5fc5e4c896fee1eb45de2","tid":538491,"uid":138225,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T16:13:04.000Z","msg":"咁我要點辭職先冇咁尷尬？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T16:16:44.000Z","msg":"如果你做得少過7日, 你可以即辭, 勞工法例保你"},{"pid":"487d781e3124ccb887cd8ff1559913c19028266a","tid":538491,"uid":8435,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bfe8c275203461fdbfe5fc5e4c896fee1eb45de2","tid":538491,"uid":138225,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T16:13:04.000Z","msg":"咁我要點辭職先冇咁尷尬？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T16:17:30.000Z","msg":"無私人嘢擺喺公司嘅話<br />\n聽朝就咁打個電話返去話唔做就得<br />\n之前公司有個返咗就嚟一個月都係咁<br />\n你做得幾日，人哋更加唔覺係咩一回事"}]}